Cape Verde beat Portugal 2-0 in a friendly on Tuesday night  . 
  The island has a population of just 500,000 people and is a former Portuguese colony . 
  Manchester United winger Nani is from the island and his mother was born there . 
  Cape Verde qualified for their first Africa Cup of Nations in 2013 . 
  Cristiano Ronaldo was rested for the friendly against Portugal . 
 